== 10. Bf4 ==
This move pins the knight on e5 to the black queen, which is its only defender at the moment. Moving the knight isn't an option, so the only move to add another defender is [[/10...Nfd7|'''10...Nfd7''']].

'''10...Bd6??''' fails to defend the knight because it loses a piece. The d6 square is attacked by both the c4 knight and the queen on d1 and only defended by Black's queen on c7.


